00:48:26.080 --> 00:48:31.840
from R Markdown, but without the requirements for R or NetR, because there's a Jupyter engine

00:48:31.840 --> 00:48:37.360
with Corto, anything that Jupyter engine can do, you know, you can do it without having this

00:48:37.360 --> 00:48:43.360
dependency on R, and from a user point of view, there's some really nice things about Corto

00:48:44.000 --> 00:48:51.040
