00:49:04.080 --> 00:49:11.679
that is it makes the syntax across all of those outputs the same, whereas with Shur Engine, it

00:49:11.679 --> 00:49:18.560
has its own syntax for making presentations that's different from an R Markdown HTML output,

00:49:18.560 --> 00:49:25.199
